         <div type="diary-day" xml:id="entry__1917-12-16">
            <p xml:space="preserve"><date when="1917-12-16">16/12</date> S.― Spaziergang <rs type="place" xml:id="pl_10798" ref="#place_388686540f35afe7790d134863d92203">Kahlenberg</rs> mit zufällig getroffnem <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52088"><roleName>Frl.</roleName> <surname>Pollak</surname></rs> 
und Bruder Landesgerichtsrath.</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">Nm. mit „<rs type="work" subtype="self" xml:id="bibl_7017">Frau des Richters</rs>“ beschäftigt.</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">Mit O. bei <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52089" ref="#person_16136"><roleName>Director</roleName> <surname>Hertzka</surname></rs>, Musikabend (<rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52090" ref="#person_13914"><surname>Brahms</surname></rs> <rs type="work" xml:id="bibl_7018">Horntrio</rs>, 
<rs type="work" xml:id="bibl_7019">Clarinettentrio</rs>, <rs type="work" xml:id="bibl_7020">Sextett B dur</rs>). <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52091" ref="#person_17496"><roleName>Frl.</roleName> <surname>Lewith</surname></rs>.― Hofr. <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_52092" ref="#person_14465"><surname>Dlabač</surname></rs> u. a.―</p>
         </div>
